# Styling Guidelines

## CSS Framework
- The project uses [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com/)
- Configuration: [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js)

## CSS Classes
- Primary button: `btn btn-primary`
- Outline button: `btn btn-outline`
- Section container: `container`
- Headline styles:
  - `headline-1` - Large hero text
  - Default headings use Tailwind's text sizing (text-xl, text-2xl, etc.)

## Icons
- Using Material Symbols Rounded
- Icon usage in components: `<span className="material-symbols-rounded">{iconName}</span>`

## Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach
- Breakpoints:
  - md: 768px
  - lg: 1024px
- Example: `class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl"`
